<br />

<br />
EQII is more soloable now then it was originally. Solo small group exp is pretty high (I two box). It may be too high, and I thought I would never say that.
<br />

<br />
I would be hard to get decent gear solo the way its set up now, unless you spent a lot of time crafting and or foraging.
<br />

<br />
A lot of folks lfg for specific quest groups.
<br />

<br />
If you read the developer letters to the general public, they make no bones about it. They are trying to gear EQII to the masses. Whatever they get the best response for, thats where they are going. If suddenly tomorrow every /feeback'ed &quot;we want red hats&quot;, I think you'd have a patch adding them within the week.
<br />

<br />
I have a friend who went with me to EQII and I think is planning on staying.
